      "content": "Choosing to disconnect from a destructive cycle is often the bravest and most necessary step toward healing, even if it feels like \"giving up.\" It's important to remember that stepping back doesn't mean you aren't trying; it means protecting your peace until you have the energy and clarity to build something truly new. If you choose to pause, let yourself do it without pressure, because your well-being is the foundation you must restore before moving forward again.",
